      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom state, exhibiting an interior and exterior finish that mirrors its original factory delivery. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, while the aesthetic remains devoid of any discernible wear. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine asset.",
