    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s basically been living in a bubble\u2014absolutely spotless inside and out, and it drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
