      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single week. It looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or dent anywhere! I\u2019m only selling because I\u2019m upgrading, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come take a look, it\u2019s even better in person!",
