      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of Porsche\u2019s widebody, naturally aspirated engineering. At its core is the 3.6L M96 flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, which has been fastidiously maintained with a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement. The drivetrain features the desirable Getrag G96 six-speed manual gearbox, delivering power through a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system for exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, equipped with Turbo-derived 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors for fade-free deceleration. With a clean DME report and zero signs of bore scoring, this C4S offers a pure, analog tactile response and peak performance metrics.",
